{"tid":2310282,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘋果報道】太陽蛋之爭｜太陽蛋一定生? (內有精液太陽蛋)","createTime":"2020-12-03T06:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T17:19:47.000Z","uid":182895,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b046a8ae7942e5f5ab59a7e56c97f4adc674e55e","tid":2310282,"uid":182895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T06:47:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">太陽蛋一定係生嘅</span></span><br />\n(cafe de jargor, 2020)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/19mhkvz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F19mhkvz.jpg&h=284f24c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想知發生咩事請睇呢到<br />\n大渣哥: 叫太陽蛋一定係生嘅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2265944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2265944</a><br />\n<br />\n想知大渣哥太陽蛋有幾勁睇呢到<br />\n[大渣哥屌打式大勝] 第一屆太陽蛋大賽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2282484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2282484</a><br />\n<br />\nFrom Apple<br />\n原link : <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20201103/AHKO7LHHWRD65CTKDMH2LEP6IE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20201103%2FAHKO7LHHWRD65CTKDMH2LEP6IE%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPcTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=76d9eebe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20201103%2FAHKO7LHHWRD65CTKDMH2LEP6IE%2F&h=f093363e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20201103/AHKO7LHHWRD65CTKDMH2LEP6IE/</a><br />\n<br />\n太陽蛋之爭｜太陽蛋一定生？ 醫生提醒食生蛋或致食物中毒 沖洗雞蛋令沙門氏菌滲入蛋內<br />\n雞蛋的營養價值高，煮法變化多，炒蛋、溏心蛋、太陽蛋等好食又方便。近日有網民投訴餐廳的太陽蛋煮得太生，引起了網民對太陽蛋做法的熱烈爭論，究竟太陽蛋係咪一定生？茶餐廳叫蛋各有不同叫法，太陽蛋一般指一面蛋黃和蛋白保持半熟狀態，另一面則全熟；荷包蛋又稱反蛋，兩面蛋白都全熟，但中間的蛋黃則呈半熟狀態。雖然人人食蛋的喜好都不同，不過其實食未熟的，分分鐘等於直接食菌落肚。<br />\n<br />\n沙門氏菌常見於動物腸道及糞便，由於雞蛋殼或沾有雞隻糞便，也是帶菌元凶，當打蛋煮食時，細菌便可污染雞蛋。另外，沙門氏菌亦可由母雞直接傳播，即是細菌會在蛋殼形成之前由受感染的生殖組織感染雞蛋。進食未煮熟的雞蛋是感染源頭，沙門氏菌不但可入侵腸道，引致腸道黏膜細胞出血，令患者有大便帶血、腹痛及發燒等症狀，也可上腦致腦膜炎，或入血引起敗血症。<br />\n<br />\n雞蛋要徹底煮熟 免疫力弱的人士盡量避免食生蛋<br />\n兒科專科醫生劉成志表示，每年都會接獲兒童感染沙門氏菌的嚴重個案。食安中心呼籲高危人士，包括孕婦、幼童、長者同免疫力弱的人士，更加不應食生或者未煮熟的蛋類菜式。食安中心更提醒大家，出門用餐時，要特別注意使用了未經徹底煮熟蛋的食物，例如芒果布甸、提拉米蘇、蛋黃醬等就最容易忽視。劉成志醫生表示，曾有2歲兒童吃下生雞蛋做的布甸後，導致沙門氏菌入血。至於半生熟的太陽蛋同樣有風險，即使蛋白全熟，但未熟的蛋黃還是可能有沙門氏菌。建議用溫度75℃以上去徹底煮熟雞蛋，細菌才可被殺死。<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"7398e0eb087f6a6db69bc957ef1cc92e580a6df2","tid":2310282,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T06:50:50.000Z","msg":"臨打蛋前都唔沖水？"},{"pid":"06ea250e0b36e111e1f0bacf2c7ea2f074d985b8","tid":2310282,"uid":281306,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T06:55:25.000Z","msg":"渣哥精液蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rsLU7eK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrsLU7eK.jpg&h=8d2ddb7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"751a90ee6e336003f0adcb2480d58e28a2a1d931","tid":2310282,"uid":182895,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06ea250e0b36e111e1f0bacf2c7ea2f074d985b8","tid":2310282,"uid":281306,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T06:55:25.000Z","msg":"渣哥精液蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rsLU7eK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrsLU7eK.jpg&h=8d2ddb7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T06:57:06.000Z","msg":"好圖<br />\n圖庫 number 1<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dade5936866a045e8912849e0c35b74d2c5b47d0","tid":2310282,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"751a90ee6e336003f0adcb2480d58e28a2a1d931","tid":2310282,"uid":182895,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06ea250e0b36e111e1f0bacf2c7ea2f074d985b8","tid":2310282,"uid":281306,"like":9,"dislike